<h1>Electronics</h1>

<ol type=1><p>

<li>Explain the theory of the transistor. Tell how transistors may be used with resistors, capacitors, and coils - in making simple circuits.<p>

<li>Do the following:
<ol type=a>
<li>Draw a simple circuit showing the resistors or tubes. Label all parts. Wire the circuit.
<li>Demonstrate the right way to solder and unsolder.
<li>Explain how to avoid heat damage to the parts.</ol><p>

<li>Explain the following:
<ol type=a>
<li>Remote-control - build a device to show how and electronic circuit is used for remote control.
<li>Electronic brain - explain the binary system of numbers. Change binary numbers to decimal numbers. Build a simple flip-flop circuit with either transistors or tubes.</ol><p>

<li>Discuss job opportunities in the field of electronics.</ol>
			
</span><p>
